        ('eef77a37-1f96-4638-bd94-6c7556993761', 'It''s important to change the default passwords on all of your assets. Check out this list of other common "Bad Practices" that might be making it easier for attackers to target your organization.', 'Bad Practices', 'article', 'https://www.cisa.gov/news-events/news/bad-practices-0'),
