        ('389ecd81-ddc0-4686-a4f9-076e7192f9b6', 'Many types of malware rely on embedded code, such as Microsoft Office macros. To keep your organization safe, these macros should be disabled by default. Read this article to learn more.', 'Macro Security For Microsoft Office', 'article', 'https://www.ncsc.gov.uk/guidance/macro-security-for-microsoft-office'),
